---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import BabyMuj from "../assets/images/baby-me.jpg";
---

<section id="about" class="col-span-full global-grid py-48 md:py-96 lg:py-160 space-y-24">
  <header class="col-span-full space-y-4 lg:space-y-8 leading-heading">
    <p class="subtext text-14 md:text-16 lg:text-18">i wanna know this guy!</p>
    <h1 class="text-32 md:text-48 lg:text-56 font-black font-sans uppercase">about &lt;me/&gt;</h1>
  </header>
  <div class="col-span-full text-16 leading-normal space-y-16 md:text-18 md:space-y-24 lg:text-20 xl:col-span-6">
    <p>
      I started out as a left brainer and enjoyed coding using <span class="font-extrabold">Java</span> and <span
        class="font-extrabold">MySQL</span
      > in the early days of high school. Couple years later I developed an addiction for web design and I&apos;m enthusiastic
      about making designs look and feel good through front-end development.
    </p>
    <p>
      I have a knack for working with <span class="font-extrabold">design systems</span>. Be it designing them from
      scratch or engineering them with the power of SCSS and Storybook.
    </p>
    <p>
      I&apos;m a cheerful person with decent marketing skills. I fancy teaching and learning anything website related
      (you should check out my IG <a href="https://instagram.com/mujs.dev" target="_blank">@mujs.dev</a>). In my spare
      time, I sleep, drink water, and hunt for trophies on my PS5.
    </p>
    <p>A brief list of tech goodies I&apos;ve been using:</p>
    <div class="space-y-16 flex flex-col text-14 md:text-16 md:flex-row md:space-y-0 md:space-x-64 lg:text-18">
      <div class="space-y-8 flex flex-col">
        <div>
          <span>👨‍🎨</span> Figma
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>👨‍🎨</span> Adobe Xd
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>👨‍🎨</span> Webflow
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>👨‍🎨</span> Stripo
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-8 flex flex-col">
        <div>
          <span>💻</span> HTML, SCSS, JS
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>💻</span> Vue, React, Next.js
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>💻</span> Storybook
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>💻</span> Handlebars
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>💻</span> Ruby on rails (a tad)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-full pt-24 space-y-16 md:pt-40 xl:pt-0 xl:col-start-8 xl:space-y-24">
    <div class="h-[400px] xl:h-[550px]">
      <Image
        src={BabyMuj}
        alt="Baby Muj in the house"
        class="saturate-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[75%] rounded-12 md:rounded-24 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out hover:saturate-100"
      />
    </div>
    <p class="subtext text-center text-12 md:text-14 lg:text-16">
      Couldn&apos;t find a cool photo. So&nbsp;here&apos;s&nbsp;a&nbsp;mini-me
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
